{"tid":1779434,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔算核彈，但都好爆：有狗扮速遞拉義士】","createTime":"2019-12-11T16:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T23:50:47.000Z","uid":122603,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d65c626af564d0b21d268f411b54f6c56aed222b","tid":1779434,"uid":122603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"有在速遞公司做高層的透露，而家正在研究點樣向公眾交代，有警察要求喬裝速遞員，上門拉義士。<br />\nUPX、DHX、FedxX，幾間大公司都牽涉其中。<br />\n因為之前警察一直有要求呢D公司合作，去拉毒販之類的犯人。<br />\n但而家佢地係咁用呢招去拉義士。<br />\n幾樣野：<br />\n1. 大家上網訂文具小心D，唔好太揚太大批貨，好易被target。<br />\n2. 速遞員上門，小心D叫佢比晒D證明，甚至影埋佢地相先。<br />\n3. 要求UPX、DHX、FedxX立即交代當中細節。<br />\n仲有冇咩野大家比下意見。"},{"pid":"7dcccb852a7ca0459f43140645b78b5fcd792e8e","tid":1779434,"uid":140218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"隻曱甴好似話仲着埋UXX制服??"},{"pid":"4c3b2994637dd4a2f257e5910f643389b664fb0b","tid":1779434,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59e28be6fad38a01073cd5d1feac863c933362b","tid":1779434,"uid":122603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7dcccb852a7ca0459f43140645b78b5fcd792e8e","tid":1779434,"uid":140218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"隻曱甴好似話仲着埋UXX制服??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"係呀，換晒衫扮鬼扮馬"},{"pid":"91dcd8e76f7f226ad2c908a3d2ceeb7cb404fc3e","tid":1779434,"uid":3522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"我覺得有需要推啲公司名上國際戰線"},{"pid":"f756d809fda99cd930a6dd790b7a9e5807b58413","tid":1779434,"uid":122603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91dcd8e76f7f226ad2c908a3d2ceeb7cb404fc3e","tid":1779434,